   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"05n.html\">一覧　（ナ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=books-jp%26keyword=%25E4%25B9%2583%25E6%259C%25A8%2520%25E5%25B8%258C%25E5%2585%25B8\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　長州藩士の三男として江戸藩邸に生まれ、萩に育つ。戊辰戦争では東北を転戦。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　西南戦争では歩兵14連隊長として出陣、軍旗を失い、かえって信頼を得る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　ドイツ留学後、日清戦争に従軍。のち、台湾総督。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　日露戦争では、第三軍を指揮し<a href=\"../1904/08ryojy.html\">旅順を攻撃</a>、甚大な被害を出す。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　のち、軍事参議官。学習院長を兼任。<a href=\"../p/mtenno.html\">明治天皇</a>の大喪儀当日、<a href=\"../1912/09jyuns.html\">妻とともに自刃</a>。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
